    "text": "We integrated multiple data sets to combine recent QTL and GWAS analyses for yield and drought resistance. This uncovered consistent genomic regions related to these traits. We determined the physical position of significant markers in the reference faba bean genome and assessed the co-localization of significant QTNs with stable QTLs, pinpointing likely candidate genes. One hundred fifty-two annotated genes in 10 overlapping genomic regions were predicted as faba bean candidate genes for drought and yield related traits. Many were closely related to genes previously identified in other crops.",
